<div class="mn-section-label">[ ACCESS DENIED ]</div>

<div class="mn-panel">
  <% if @message == "not_on_allowlist" %>
    <p>your hack club auth login worked, but you're not on mnemosyne's staff list yet. ping whoever runs this thing.</p>
  <% else %>
    <p>something went wrong signing in (<%= @message %>). try again?</p>
  <% end %>

  <%= link_to "back to login", login_path, class: "mn-link inline-block mt-4" %>
</div>
